## Response Format

All search results follow the **MCBaseItem** contract:

```json
{
  "mc_id": "tmdb_tv_1396",
  "mc_type": "tv",
  "mc_subtype": null,
  "source": "tmdb",
  "source_id": "1396",
  "search_title": "Breaking Bad",
  "year": 2008,
  "popularity": 156.789,
  "rating": 8.9,
  "image": "https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/...",
  "cast": ["Bryan Cranston", "Aaron Paul", ...],
  "genres": ["Drama", "Crime"],
  "overview": "A high school chemistry teacher diagnosed with..."
}
```

